 <span data-ttu-id="66536-236">Cette méthode accepte les objets répertoriés ci-dessus pour le `builder` paramètre.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="66536-236">This method accepts the objects listed above for the `builder` parameter.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="66536-237">Pour plus d’informations, consultez le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> et <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> opérateurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="66536-237">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
