 <span data-ttu-id="66536-291">`builder` est ajouté à la fin de la séquence en cours d’éléments de syntaxe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="66536-291">`builder` is added to the end of the current sequence of grammar elements.</span></span>  
  
